questionsAndAnswers.question: What details do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need your domain & hosting login info with website content that includes logo, images, and text.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
No, I do not provide domain & hosting service directly I can refer you to the best service provider.
You can have a look here https://cutt.ly/bh-host

questionsAndAnswers.question: Am I able to make changes after completing the website if I don't have the coding experience?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can do that but you need to learn page builder a bit. I will provide you with a reference video tutorial to make changes.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If need any support in the future do you provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide you with 15 days of Free after-sale service and will get lifetime paid service as well.
